Àtụ:Infobox badminton player
Anuoluwapo Juwon Opeyori (amuru 1 June 1997) bu onye egwu badminton nke Naijiria
Ọ malitere na-egwu egwu badminton ya na nwanne ya na 2005, ma emesịa ahọpụtara ya ka ọ sonyere ndị otu egwuregwu mba Nigeria na 2017
Opeyori meriri asọmpi mba Afrịka na egwuregwu Afrịka na mmemme ndi otu na 2019
Ọ gbara asọmpi na Summer Olympics 2020
